title: '"VAT on fixed assets: VAT has to be paid on investment in fixed assets, but businesses cannot obtain a refund against output VAT for the input VAT paid on the investment. As from 2019 onwards, the unrecoverable VAT can be recovered in the form of a CIT credit."'
